.container.content
  %h1 Song position
  %h4
    Don't worry folks if there are blanks below and you picked the song, just some auto matching from the triplej twitter feed issues
    you will have the score added to your total and you can check out under your picks
-##myfirstchart

%table.table.table-striped
  %tr
    %th Position
    %th Song
    %th Picks
    %th Tweet

  - @tweets.each do |tweet|
    %tr
      %td= tweet.position
      %td
        = link_to tweet.song.name, song_users_path(tweet.song) if tweet.song
      %td= tweet.song.selections.length if tweet.song
      %td= tweet.status

